data.title: Military Ordinariate of Ordinariato Castrense de Portugal, Portugal
data.meta_description: It has been vacant since 2023.08 when Patriarch Rui Manuel Sousa Valério, S.M.M. was transferred, with Patriarch Rui Manuel Sousa Valério, S.M.M. acting as apostolic administrator of the military ordinariate.
